00:49:55.630 --> 00:49:57.630
Psalm 84 11 says,

00:49:57.630 --> 00:50:00.630
Jehovah will not hold back anything good

00:50:00.630 --> 00:50:03.630
from those walking in integrity.

00:50:03.630 --> 00:50:05.630
When we show our complete,

00:50:05.630 --> 00:50:08.630
wholehearted devotion to God by obeying Him

00:50:08.630 --> 00:50:10.630
